scenes.description: A satirical infomercial for Mori Calliope's birthday merchandise, featuring a high-energy announcer and eventually Mori herself.
Mori Calliope appears on stage to talk to the audience about the merchandise and a new announcement.
Mori introduces a trailer for her 'NEW UNDERWORLD ORDER' LIVE Blu-ray release.
